{"tid":1334784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文促國際支持香港追求民主聲音","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T08:51:08.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c4f029e57deeec6aad919ece59deeefd77edbe9c","tid":1334784,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"台灣總統蔡英文結束在加勒比海友邦的訪問，回程期間過境美國丹佛，停留兩晚。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文與美國國會參議院外交委員會亞太小組主席賈德納(Cory Gardner)會面時談及香港，認為香港民眾追求民主自由的聲音，國際社會應給予更多的聲援與支持。美國與台灣共享價值，應該在香港議題上有更多的合作，表達對香港問題的關注。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文又感謝美方支持對台軍售；賈德納稱，美國國會會持續關注台海安全情勢、持續支持對台軍售案，協助台灣提升自我防衞能力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2196490/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2196490%2F&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=fe29f974\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2196490/</a>"},{"pid":"e30ceefca33c2d7bbab40c9db98b146bf14e3f79","tid":1334784,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"多謝Vegetable English助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}